## Why This Is Asked
Explores dynamic extensibility and runtime hot-swapping of behavior without redeployments, crucial for scalable data platforms.

## Key Concepts
- Plugin registry mapping (type, version) to handlers
- Versioned command schemas and graceful deprecation
